<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/home.css">
  <title>SamSocial</title>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Portrait -->
  <div class="portrait">
    <h1>This website is currently unavailable on your screen.</h1>
  </div>

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="content">
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Splash content -->
    <img src="images/home/splash.jpg" class="splash-image">
    <h1 class="splash-h1">Samaritan Social</h1>

    <!-- Feature Cards -->
    <div class="feature-cards-container">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <p>As a nonprofit, we are solely dedicated to making a positive impact in communities worldwide by providing support and resources to those in need. Our mission is to promote social good and create meaningful connections among individuals and organizations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <p>Join us in our mission to make the world a better place. Whether you're an individual looking to volunteer or an organization seeking partnership opportunities, Samaritan Social is here to help you make a difference.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <p>Together, we can create positive change and build a brighter future for all. Join Samaritan Social today and be a part of something meaningful.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Statement -->
    <div class="mission-statement">
      <div class="mission-left">
        <h1>Our mission</h1>
        <p>Here at Samaritan Social, we believe that it is our mission to unite people and service organizations around the globe. We aim to connect individuals with opportunities to give back to their communities and support those in need. Our vision is a world where compassion and service are at the forefront of society, making the world a better place for all.</p>
        <p>Join us in our mission to create positive change and promote social good. Together, we can make a significant impact and build a better future for everyone.</p>
        <br><br>
        <p style="float:right;">-The SamSocial Team</p>
      </div>
      <img src="/images/home/mission-statement.jpg">
      <button onclick="location.href='register'">Start today!</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Partners -->
    <div class="partners-container">
      <!-- Only have 6 partners at a time -->
      <div class="partner partner-1">
        <img src="https://www.freeiconspng.com/thumbs/leaf-icon-png/green-leaf-icon-10.png">
        <div class="partner-text">
          <h1>GreenGlow Initiative</h1>
          <p>GreenGlow Initiative provides eco-friendly energy alternatives to underprivileged areas, distributing solar kits and training residents in renewable energy technologies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="partner partner-2">
        <img src="https://static.thenounproject.com/png/562360-200.png">
        <div class="partner-text">
          <h1>CodeBridge Alliance</h1>
          <p>CodeBridge offers free coding and tech workshops to underserved communities, helping them unlock careers in the growing tech industry.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="partner partner-3">
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/12/12638.png">
        <div class="partner-text">
          <h1>Paws of Hope Network</h1>
          <p>A global organization that uses innovative matching systems to pair abandoned pets with perfect foster and forever homes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="partner partner-4">
        <img src="https://icons.veryicon.com/png/o/miscellaneous/fine-linear-ico/water-drop-4.png">
        <div class="partner-text">
          <h1>WellSpring Collective</h1>
          <p>WellSpring builds water purification systems and delivers health education programs to remote villages in need of clean drinking water.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="partner partner-5">
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/493/493808.png">
        <div class="partner-text">
          <h1>YouthRoots Empowerment Corps</h1>
          <p>YouthRoots provides mentorship and funding to young entrepreneurs with community-oriented projects, emphasizing sustainability and innovation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="partner partner-6">
        <img src="https://pngimg.com/d/smiley_PNG149.png">
        <div class="partner-text">
          <h1>Stitching Smiles Foundation</h1>
          <p>An arts-focused nonprofit that supplies fabric, tools, and sewing workshops to marginalized artisans, fostering self-sufficiency and creativity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Organization Join -->

    <div class="org-join-bg">
      <div class="org-join">
        <div class="org-join-text">
          <h1>Looking to join?</h1>
          <p>As an organization, you can join us as a partner by becoming part of our mission to make a positive impact in communities around the world. Whether you're a nonprofit, charity, or service organization, we welcome you to join our network of change-makers.</p>
          <p>To join, click the button below and fill out the form. After you submit, we'll review your application and get in touch with you.</p>
          <button onclick="location.href='register'">Join Us!</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer (thank goodness I'm done) -->
    <footer>
      <div class="footer-text">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Samaritan Social</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </div>

  <script src="scripts/home/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>